      description: `Kate Roberts is our Operations Supervisor and licensed Commercial Pilot with a degree Aviation Management from Auburn University. With a strong foundation in aviation operations, safety compliance, and coordination, Kate combines hands-on leadership with technical expertise.  Kate is passionate about operational excellence and fostering the next generation of aviation professionals.`,
